Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:11.69,ed - cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.25\fad(300,300)}“0”是過去 “1”是未來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:22.84,ed - jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2.25\fad(300,300)}並行する無數の線
